{
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "kind": "module",
  "key": "menu_view_lcd1602_adapter",
  "display_name": "Menu View LCD1602 Adapter",
  "summary": "Character-LCD render bridge that maps one MenuView instance onto a 2x16 LCD1602 display.",
  "hal_components": [],
  "template_files": [
    "modules/menu_view_lcd1602_adapter.c",
    "modules/menu_view_lcd1602_adapter.h"
  ],
  "resource_requests": [],
  "depends_on": [
    "menu_view",
    "lcd1602_i2c"
  ],
  "init_priority": 80,
  "loop_priority": 80,
  "c_callbacks_template": [
    "void MenuView_OnRender(const MenuView *view)",
    "{",
    "    char line0[17];",
    "    char line1[17];",
    "    if (!MenuView_Matches(view, \"[[dep_menu_view_module_name]]\")) {",
    "        return;",
    "    }",
    "    MenuViewLcd1602_FormatLine(view, 0U, line0, sizeof(line0));",
    "    MenuViewLcd1602_FormatLine(view, 1U, line1, sizeof(line1));",
    "    (void)LCD1602_SetCursor(&[[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_handle]], [[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_address_macro]], 0U, 0U, [[option_timeout_ms|100]]);",
    "    (void)LCD1602_WriteString(&[[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_handle]], [[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_address_macro]], line0, [[option_timeout_ms|100]]);",
    "    (void)LCD1602_SetCursor(&[[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_handle]], [[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_address_macro]], 1U, 0U, [[option_timeout_ms|100]]);",
    "    (void)LCD1602_WriteString(&[[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_handle]], [[dep_lcd1602_i2c_i2c_address_macro]], line1, [[option_timeout_ms|100]]);",
    "}"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "Override MenuViewLcd1602_FormatLine(...) to customize the two rendered LCD rows without re-implementing MenuView_OnRender(...).",
    "Use only one MenuView render adapter per MenuView instance, because each adapter owns the global MenuView_OnRender callback."
  ],
  "sources": [
    "Menu rendering on HD44780-compatible 2x16 displays."
  ]
}
